{
  "stem": "16163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think he work-- worked in the basement where they sorted potatoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he would steal potatoes, cook them, and bring them to the hospital to me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Then my grandmother was very sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother took care till the last minute of her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she died in February '43-- 1943.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I still was in the hospital at that time, so they came to tell me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGH] I think she died of old age, number one, and hunger, and not being in a house, not being home, and not having her [POINTS] comfort-- that way.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very funny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I dreamt two days before-- two nights before my grandmother died, I dreamt that my mother-- grandmother died.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when my mother and father came to tell me, I told them that I knew already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now I break up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] That's it-- one of those psychic things I think can happen to anybody in life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It really wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew [? it ?] already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was amazing what these people did for me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because if not for them, I-- I would have died a long time before even anything else happened there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They really did-- [BACKROUND NOISE] there were three doctors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were three doctors, who individually took care of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] There were two doctors-- actually all three of them were from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schwartz from [INAUDIBLE], and one was Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Haiek from [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Prague, and one was Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Zonzhavic, which was a woman, from-- also from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And between the three of them, they tried everything and anything to take care of me and the other children who were there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of children died right next to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
